title: Crowds contribute almost £50,000 to Airshow costs (Tendring District Council)
text: ( Source : Tendring District Council ) Record crowds at Clacton Airshow helped contribute almost £50, 000 towards the running costs of the popular event. Around 220 ,000 people watched the two day spectacular in August which boasted its best
